thread.title_full: Pack Mule reviewed by Michael Catsburg Johnston Equipment

author: Michael Catsburg Johnston Equipment
title: Michael Catsburg Johnston Equipment
text:
Thank you so much for providing timely design and costing estimates to assist us in our proposal to supply 7 Quad steer true tracing trailers
The Pack Mule solution was superior in quality and options offered as well as a much better delivery for the end user as compared to other units in the market The base capacity far exceeded similar units at the same price point. Added Value ? Call Pack Mule !.
